--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                              CHEF Demo Portlet 

			      Version VERSION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This ia CHEF demo portlet.


PREREQUISITES:
--------------

1. GNU tar (or ensure that your tar can handle paths longer than 100
   characters long)

2. Jakarta Ant (we use version 1.5 but it will probably work with most earlier
   versions too) - http://jakarta.apache.org/ant

INSTALL:
--------

To install the CHEF demo portlet into your iNGS/Chef portal, you'll need
to: 

1.  Untar and unzip portlet-demo-VERSION-[src,bin].tar.gz.

2.  Define chef.home in file build.properties.

3.  For binary distribution, execute:

      ant deploy

    For source distribution, execute:

      ant build deploy

4.  Restart your portal


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
